{"tid":1550571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵會害死大量手足","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T16:28:49.000Z","uid":282414,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"71adcc53b1cf889c61bbf021fa17d40c858493da","tid":1550571,"uid":282414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:38:09.000Z","msg":"太古站瘋狂推人落樓梯，太子站無差別打人，到今日大埔墟站濫捕<br />\n<br />\n大家明白未呀？？？PK 黨鐵會害死你，你一沉醉破壞部入閘機，就叫警犬咬死你！！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>黨鐵要避之則吉，你玩破壞公物都要搵定後路。</strong>"},{"pid":"4b3c4507169112a6db0c962842ebd99457801605","tid":1550571,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:38:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31d4274462067bd7f707b645e1ed52c7c5f8902d","tid":1550571,"uid":7738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:40:53.000Z","msg":"唯快不破"},{"pid":"3ae7c9e369f1d3fc23638cf2100a51e3ca6f202e","tid":1550571,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:49:48.000Z","msg":"倒廁所水玩機快狠準"},{"pid":"ae37e46fc40231b36cb6fea61c8faf7b6133d2ff","tid":1550571,"uid":275884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2